\sin u\cos v=\frac{1}{2}[\sin (u+v)+\sin(u-v)]
\cos u \sin v=\frac{1}{2}[\sin(u+v)-\sin(u-v)]
\sin (u+v) = \sin (v+u)
\sin (u-v)=-\sin (v-u)
